    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>Y68.22 Var. a (mss. 5, 40, 88, 400, 410, 2005, 2101, 2102, 2106, 4000, 4010, 4020, 4050, 4060, 4162, 5020):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>humatanąm ... vohunąm mahī</em> dō bār guftan āb az ǰām ō ī dudīgar gyāg pad pādyāb rēxtan</ab>  
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "They should recite twice the stanza <em>humatanąm ... vohunąm mahī</em>.  (The <em>zōt</em>) has to pour the water from one cup to another container with <em>pādyāb</em>."</ab>
            <ab>Y68.22 Var. b (mss. 6, 15, 82, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2104, 4056): </ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>humatanąm ... vohunąm mahī</em> dō bār guftan ǰām purr az āb bē kunišn ud āb az ǰām ō ī dudīgar ǰām ī pādyābdān kardan</ab>  
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "They should recite twice the stanza <em>humatanąm ... vohunąm mahī</em>. (The <em>zōt</em>) has to fill the cup with water and bring the water from one cup to the cup <em>pādyābdān</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
